      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, currently held in pristine, showroom condition. This specimen has been curated for the most discerning collector, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from its original delivery state. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and reliability. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a benchmark-quality vehicle that reflects a legacy of meticulous ownership and uncompromising care.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
