    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in showroom condition, reflecting meticulous ownership and an uncompromising commitment to preservation. Every detail, from the pristine interior surfaces to the flawless mechanical integration, confirms its status as a premier acquisition for the discerning driver. We invite serious inquiries to experience a vehicle that defines the pinnacle of its class.",
