      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, you\u2019ve got to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
