    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera 4S is a superlative example of the wide-body aesthetic paired with a pure analog driving experience. Powered by a 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus, the power delivery remains linear and robust across the entire rev range. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise, tactile engagement, while the viscous-clutch AWD system ensures optimal torque distribution. This specimen features a documented IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement, addressing critical mechanical longevity. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec suspension geometry, and the four-piston monoblock Brembo calipers provide immediate, fade-free deceleration. Meticulously preserved with original paint and a pristine undercarriage, this is a turnkey, collector-grade vehicle for the discerning purist.",
